Use Alembic from this directory.

Commands
- Generate initial migration (autogenerate):
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5444/chat alembic revision --autogenerate -m "init"
- Apply to head:
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5444/chat alembic upgrade head

Notes
- env.py targets `app.models.Base` for autogenerate. Review diffs before applying.
